You must at least provide the keyfile and certfile as well:

```python
@bentoml.service(
    ssl={"enabled": True, "keyfile": "private.key", "certfile": "cert.pem"}
)
```

Also if the key pairs are self-signed, turn on the insecure mode on the client. But since the bentoml built-in client doesn't support insecure mode, you will need to use your own client instead.

